Sentence: Bruck Dawit is an Ethiopian-American musician, music producer, record mixer, composer and author.
Bruck Dawit and his writing partner the singer France Gall, wrote the musical Résiste.
The musical had its first representation on November 4, 2015 at the Palais des Sports auditorium in Paris, France.
